<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 01:24:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在中东交易乐观情绪中，比特币攀升至两个月高点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-17/bitcoin-climbs-to-two-month-high-amid-middle-east-deal-optimism</link><description>在美国和伊朗的一系列言论引发人们对中东冲突可能走向解决的乐观情绪后，比特币升至二月初以来的最高水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1a4XQcF.MSo/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 14:55:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-17/bitcoin-climbs-to-two-month-high-amid-middle-east-deal-optimism</guid></item><item><title>比特币的脆弱复苏带来了巨大的空头挤压风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/bitcoin-s-fragile-recovery-sets-up-a-big-short-squeeze-risk</link><description>比特币恢复到 75,000 美元以上存在一个可信度问题：拥有最大杠杆的交易者不相信它。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/icRqRqGOtKPw/v0/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 20:35:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/bitcoin-s-fragile-recovery-sets-up-a-big-short-squeeze-risk</guid></item><item><title>法国当局在绑架狂潮后保护加密货币高管</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/french-authorities-shield-crypto-execs-after-kidnapping-spree</link><description>法国当局正试图安抚紧张不安的数字资产高管和投资者，因为一系列绑架和绑架未遂事件可能会颠覆该国的加密中心雄心。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iB2kAfooVPD0/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 16:31:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/french-authorities-shield-crypto-execs-after-kidnapping-spree</guid></item><item><title>Flow Capital 将 1.5 亿美元私人信贷基金置于区块链上</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-17/flow-capital-puts-150-million-private-credit-fund-on-blockchain</link><description>Flow Capital Partners 计划于月底前在新加坡的区块链平台上发行其 1.5 亿美元的私人信贷基金，从而将自己定位为首批利用不断增长的稳定币流动性的亚洲管理公司之一。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iet4.SRd8w1g/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 02:13:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-17/flow-capital-puts-150-million-private-credit-fund-on-blockchain</guid></item></channel></rss>